      "span_text": "Randomization resulted in four experimental groups: (1) sham umbilical cord occlusion, saline treatment (sham-SAL n = 8), [CITATION_1] sham umbilical cord occlusion, MAPC treatment (sham-MAPC; n = 8), (3) umbilical cord occlusion, saline treatment (HI-SAL; n = 8), and (4) umbilical cord occlusion, MAPC treatment (HI-MAPC; n = 8) (Fig. 1) .",
